{"itemid":1854,"subject":"Nebula Nominees","event":"SFWA has announced the finalists for this year's Nebula Awards.\r\n\r\nYou can find the full list on the SFWA website, here:  https://www.sfwa.org/2016/02/2015-nebula-awards-nominees-announced/\r\n\r\nCongratulations to all the nominees... and to our new Grand Master, C.J. Cherryh.\r\n\r\nAnd a special shout-out to David D. Levine, who is one of my Wild Cards writers.  David is a finalist in Short Story for \"Damage,\" from Tor.com.\r\n\r\nBut speaking of David... do watch Tor.com for his next story, a Wild Cards original entitled \"Discards.\"  It will be up on Tor.com in March, with an amazing John Picacio \"cover.\"\r\n\r\n<img src=\"http://ic.pics.livejournal.com/grrm/7059164/338313/338313_800.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\">\r\n\r\n\"Discards\" is set in Rio, and introduces David's new Brazilian ace, The Recycler.  I think you'll like it.","ditemid":474729,"eventtime":"2016-02-25 14:52:00","props":{"current_mood":"pleased","current_location":"Santa Fe","taglist":"tor, wild cards, awards","crosspost_tw_log":"[Mon Feb 22 21:51:44 2016]R [Mon Feb 22 21:51:46 2016]https://twitter.com/GRRMspeaking/status/701887127039004673 ","current_moodid":109,"commentalter":1456352774,"opt_lockcomments":1,"crosspost_tw":"https://twitter.com/GRRMspeaking/status/701887127039004673","picture_keyword":"happy blue","opt_screening":"F","revnum":2,"personifi_tags":"nterms:yes","interface":"web","langs":"{\"languages\":[[\"eng\",0.641319816570418]],\"detector\":\"Lingua-YALI:0.015\",\"updated\":1456177915}","revtime":1457077219},"can_comment":0,"logtime":"2016-02-22 21:51:44","anum":105,"url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/474729.html","event_timestamp":1456411920,"reply_count":9,"comments":[{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"userpic":"http://l-userpic.livejournal.com/120472665/62343142","actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/474729.html?thread=24046953#t24046953","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.l